    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The resolution of electronic imaging devices such as computer monitors, digital cameras, televisions, or scanners, expressed as the number of pixels per linear inch. Pixels per centimeter also describes the resolution of image files.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
